Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然停了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊 还用怀表？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特别的日子 所以找出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别的日子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这岛上有钟表店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止当我们这儿是孤岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君还没去过商店街那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在今天之内修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我今天就带你上街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤岛的街啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来约会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 那怀表为什么一定要今天修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有点原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像木头棒子似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是碰到毒蛇就用那棒子吓走它免得被咬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 还真有孤岛风范
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 竟然有剧场还有新潮的书店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买色情杂志的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我在外面等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何收获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱岛上秩序的人 决不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衬衫 蛮适合须方的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 是须方君的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 须方君不喜欢过生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「须方」是进藤家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每代生就带有印记的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能取的特别的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君知道自己的身世和素体的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是5年前的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 他好像就很讨厌自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方也能驾驶素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君的 有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn那些是战士的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继承的是巫女的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 进藤家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君继承的是王的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量大概是这个星球最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的素体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那台素体多半坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是不能驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体虽然不能动 却可以驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驭者将会获得强力的第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一阶段…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子夫人的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姿色和商业才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是第一阶段的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是这样也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由驯化产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在零时空间以外也能使用的素体之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是第一阶段的定义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不一定是超常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社会上突然大获成功的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是将第一阶段的力量据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能如果被社会认同也算幸福的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异能的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只会让持有者遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巫女的我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方同学想离开是可以离开岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了避免那强大的力量在外部使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君也被禁止离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这孤岛所困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方拥有什么力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拥有印记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是须方君没有驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化王之素体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下记录的几乎所有驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在使用了被称为王之柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强力第一阶段力量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入深沉的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷茶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个轻浮女和那外乡人发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会失去巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能坐视计划继续被拖延了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还无法控制自己的第一阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰别人谈恋爱就太不解风情了
