Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言是重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和须方君 从小相识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在这里的皆水神社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了封印巫女的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知命中注定无法离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却能坚持到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是因为有背负着同样命运的须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 总是随身携带着小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直害怕 不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候须方君生日宴会上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他戴着我送的玻璃珠项链
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提多高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是他的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能对他说生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年在其他日子 找其他理由送出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的生日成为讨厌的纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想利用拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他庆祝生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这座岛上要有素体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要生在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去把礼物交给须方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷今天不见任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己一个人关在道场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方在不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有须方君的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这是我给须方的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 也是给自己的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿唱首歌好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:02.32,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:07.09,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:11.77,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:19.90,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,600)}此刻 世界转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.99,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暖暖的艳阳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:29.50,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}花蕾含苞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:39.40,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(424,470)}微睡中 感受喜悦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险又漆黑的夜海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆手持鱼叉 发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无法用语言叙述的激烈战斗过后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死乌贼大王的萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于获得了那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 没有战斗场景描写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼大王的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓶中煌煌生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了夜色的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满神秘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着这瓶青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆得以晋见国王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王大人 这是约定的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王激动得浑身发抖 接过瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口喝下了那瓶青色液体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被施以不老不死的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来结束他永恒人生的唯一解药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜入眠后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便也不会再次醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意料的剧情展开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果汁 不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 萨姆怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊人胃口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游弋吧 美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等前来相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水大人请隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么 温蒂尼（Ondine）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 犯规也得有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪快 银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了 温蒂尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让它做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水巫女也在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美人鱼自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深层意识的暴走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's a pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王之柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 成为了我们无法忘却的纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}须方！
