Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:24:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化最强王之素体的须方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入深沉的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方 快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 必会闪耀
